Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接近猫咪的第一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以和它对视
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第二点 要把身体放低
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:15.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你明白我没有敌意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第三点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:25.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,慢慢地接近它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,多亏了昨天在电视上看到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我竟然能走到离它这么近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明差点就能摸到猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是在撸猫的时候被她发现真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是真被她看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片在撸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,身为男孩子居然喜欢可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:52.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不能再增加会被高木同学捉弄的因素了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你喜欢猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:02:59.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,糟了 一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:05.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太天真了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猫咪的警惕性可是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那样做完全不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么那么随便也可以把猫叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学难道是驯猫大师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你今天也很可爱呢 咪太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你认识的猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 这只猫是我家隔壁婆婆养的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 害我瞎着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这孩子最喜欢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以随便摸个够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,摸个够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以撸猫撸到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也来摸摸看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你刚才打算去摸猫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且还在用昨天电视上的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:16.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是想试试电视上的方法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以你其实不喜欢猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也不怎么想碰猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猫咪明明很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毛蓬松松的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肉垫也软乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这家伙甚至能让人摸肉垫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好想摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是现在才说想摸什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是搞不懂那些想撸猫的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的有那么可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算退一百步来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也不至于想要摸它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为那可是动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁知道会突然它会干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:11.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你嘴上这么说 其实是怕被抓伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我现在就证明我敢摸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗 抱歉怀疑你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的表情太明显了吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也太想撸猫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你是要摸呢还是不摸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以摸摸它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过咪太已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 什么时候不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们现在去找猫吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,佐藤她好像喜欢三班的田中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我也觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也想聊恋爱话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜欢什么类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说得太突然了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢会向我撒娇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:37.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我比较喜欢体格魁梧 毛比较长的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 真是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,能行 她们俩能聊上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚就在聊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知不觉就聊起了这种话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 问一些更深层的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉喜欢什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你终于问到这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的是长腿帅气那种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗原来很执着于头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和早苗一样 长的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:08.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这个 我想和朋友聊的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就是苏俄猎狼犬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错没错 苏俄猎狼犬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 是在说狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你喜欢的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢吉娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 和你刚才说的不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 吉娃娃也有长毛的品种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要画人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自由绘画难道不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你有认真看着我画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:21.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果太专注画画 作画的时间容易比观察的时间长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:27.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之要看 观察的时间要是画画的一倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,老师是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 她怎么笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我脸上沾了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:50.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 课间在厕所照镜子的时候什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,头发睡乱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 这个也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 她笑的是我的长相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我能有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷静 不冷静下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错 肯定是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,打算看我忐忑不安的样子来取乐吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看我原封不动地还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,画得太烂 连自己都笑出声了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是我的脸上沾了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没想到她会拿自己的事问我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以我不是说了吗 美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的眼角才没有这么吊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但感觉上就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别靠感觉画 给我看仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 这个是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你给我就是这样的感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就这样跟她说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 还剩十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,糟了 做的太过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:35.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 我按感觉画就画成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是什么 高木同学 你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我肚子好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然要乱画的话 至少画成这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来 你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:57.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看不清的话就靠近点呗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,仔细看高木同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可…可…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的脸有那么偏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的脸才没有那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始一直很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有 是你自己这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,仔细看看 哪里红了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是这张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的愿望大体上都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈也来试试嘛 恋爱占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:13.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很准的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实你是想自己来占卜吧 由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:22.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也太易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说我是为了美奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好想快点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:31.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要来猜拳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,输的人回家路上请喝果汁 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然听起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我还要留下来扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我等你做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用了 这样多不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那要是西片赢了 我就帮你打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么想玩猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我倒是没所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:13.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不许用提前宣布自己要出什么这种精神攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:20.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可连续输过四次给高木同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,赢 赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次猜赢高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 你肯定很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉没让她吃到什么苦头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就让我沉浸在首胜的愉悦之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你相信占卜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 为什么会这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天大家都去占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是刚才那些像扑克一样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是塔罗牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我今天用它做了恋爱占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说我现在的恋情能顺利发展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在的恋情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我问你 你有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有 没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:46.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么她会在这种时候问那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我为什么会这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:11.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜欢高木同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚才我之所以问你有没有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是在给西片做恋爱占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 难道我现在很失落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后 结果是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你有喜欢的人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我在努力打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,赶紧岔开这个话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们还占卜了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片会在猜拳出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 你是指刚才我赢了的那场猜拳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 果然也不过只是占卜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,耿耿于怀的我真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是因为你信什么占卜才不得不来做扫除啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,活该 活该
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我猜中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 快点打扫吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,438)}高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(524,592)}欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(524,682)}安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(524,770)}逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(524,858)}捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.64,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1645.8,651)}西片出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.77,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1560,729.2)}西片好像很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1558.4,663.6)}高木同学使用了捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:41.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1585.6,732.4)}西片受到了暴击！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1632,660.4)}西片被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.98,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1553.6,730.8)}西片果然很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我一定要战胜高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉你心情不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么都不知道真是轻松啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的我可是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟在早上的星座占卜里 我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为早上的星座占卜里巨蟹座排第一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道我属巨蟹座
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为我和你说了生日快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来有这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但为什么她连占卜的事情都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为今天的血型占卜里我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 O型血也是第一名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道我是O型血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没想到她居然能猜到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天真的其实是我才对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在两个占卜里都是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以产生了最强的气场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是有什么好事发生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我走着瞧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的我运气是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天被捉弄的次数是五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要做一百五十个俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为占卜结果不错就忘乎所以的我简直就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 因为没有好事发生所以很消沉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟只是个占卜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明你自己也在用塔罗牌占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:55.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明明一直在想能战胜高木同学的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,结果却什么也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也许今天还是放弃为好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:05.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不如说这样结束已经算是美好的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对 不能就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:19.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 你在占卜的地方写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是说占卜留言那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一名是巨蟹座 一定会出现暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:29.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了 会出现暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说会出现一击逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被捉弄数十次之后 只要能捉弄到高木同学一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是我的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要放弃啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 你到底写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 到底写了什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天是爆裂足球的游戏发售日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去他家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:13.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爆裂足球吗 好想玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 怎么能在暴击来到前回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但还真是头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一点头绪都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我能想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可是今天最幸运的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不去打游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:37.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想和高木同学一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有没有什么主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:47.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 我刚才是不是说了什么奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为占卜里说会出现暴击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以我才想着今天一定能赢过高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以不是你想的那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:14.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这还有什么暴击 直接自爆了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:20.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以 刚才的话你就当作没听见吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要是再说一次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就当作没有听见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么说得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:58.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴击真可怕呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:55.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.91,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:10.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:19.10,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:27.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:51.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:59.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:05.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:19.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:55.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.91,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:10.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:19.10,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:27.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:35.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:51.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:59.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:05.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:19.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:20.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「ねえ、大好きな君へ」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.90,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}笑わないで聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:28.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「愛してる」だなんてクサいけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:31.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけど　この言葉以外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:34.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}伝える事が出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:39.88,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほらね　またバカにして笑ったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:51.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}君の選んだ人生（ミチ）は僕（ココ）で良かったのかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.47,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}分からないけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:59.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただ泣いて笑って　過ごす日々に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:05.86,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}隣に立って　居れることで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:11.24,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}僕が生きる　意味になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:17.08,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}泣き笑い悲しみ喜びを共に分かち合い生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いくつもの 夜を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:30.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}僕は君と 愛を唄おう
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:20.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 致我最喜欢的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.90,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}听的时候不许发笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:28.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「我爱你」什么的虽然很俗套
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:31.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但是 这些话语以外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:34.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}再没有什么能传达我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:39.88,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 又要把我当成傻瓜来笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:51.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}虽然不知道 你把我视为人生的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:54.47,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}究竟是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:59.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}哭着笑着走过的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:05.86,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}能够待在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:11.24,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就是我活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:17.08,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}分享着彼此的喜怒哀乐 一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}跨越无数个黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:30.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你我二人 共唱我们的情歌吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
